cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.PL, cs.SE, cs.FL

Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper discusses formal synthesis, which is a topic closely related to logic and automated reasoning. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper discusses inductive learning, which is a subfield of AI. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is relevant as the paper discusses the process of generating a program satisfying a high-level formal specification. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is relevant as the paper discusses the practical impact of the oracle-guided inductive synthesis framework. 
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is relevant as the paper discusses learning any program that computes a recursive language.
